    Browser <-->|HTTP| React
    React <-->|REST API| FastAPI
    FastAPI <-->|Queue Tasks| Redis
    FastAPI <-->|CRUD| SQLite
    FastAPI <-->|Save/Load| FileStorage
    Redis <-->|Consume Tasks| Celery
    Celery -->|Process Video| OpenCV
    OpenCV -->|Frames| MediaPipe
    MediaPipe -->|Face ROI| FER
    Celery <-->|Read/Write| FileStorage
    Celery <-->|Update Status| SQLite
